Barclays, Absa Group to Focus on Aligning Their African Operations in 2011

-- B y   R e n e e   B o n o r c h i s
-- 
2011-02-15T06:26:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-15/barclays-absa-group-to-focus-on-aligning-their-african-operations-in-2011.html
  Absa Group Ltd . Chief Executive
Officer  Maria Ramos  said aligning  South Africa ’s largest retail
bank and its parent Barclays Plc in  Africa  is a “key priority”
for 2011.  She was speaking on a conference call with reporters today
from Johannesburg. The lender expects to spend 5 billion rand on
its information technology systems in 2011, Ramos said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Renee Bonorchis in Johannesburg at 
 rbonorchis@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
